# Backend (Cloudflare Workers) kept PRIVATE, not in the public repo. Local copies stay on disk for
# deploys; never re-track them. (Owner decision 2026-06-21: backend source must not be public.)
/cloudflare/
/cloudflare-ratings/
/cloudflare-poster/
/cloudflare-erdb/

# --- build artifacts & deps (reconstructed by scripts/build-web.sh) ---
web/
**/node_modules/
**/build/
**/DerivedData/
**/.build/

# --- translation export artifact (regenerated by the i18n tooling; never tracked) ---
/translations_out.json

# --- packaged outputs ---
*.ipa
*.xcarchive
*.dSYM.zip

# --- generated Xcode project (produced by XcodeGen from app/project.yml) ---
app/*.xcodeproj

# --- reference IPAs (Stremio's proprietary binaries, never commit) ---
reference/

# --- vendored nodejs-mobile (downloaded by scripts; ~51MB) ---
app/Vendor/

# --- bundled streaming server (extracted from Stremio's macOS app; proprietary) ---
app/Resources/server.js

# --- standalone node binary for the macOS streaming server (downloaded by
#     scripts/fetch-node-macos.sh; ~95MB; nodejs-mobile has no macOS slice) ---
app/Resources/node-darwin-arm64

# --- edge-signing secret (build-time HMAC key for the hardened VortX edge workers) ---
#     The repo is PUBLIC; this real xcconfig must NEVER be committed (a secret in git history is
#     leaked forever). Only the committed *.example template is tracked. Owner provisions the real
#     value locally here + as a CI GitHub repo secret. See app/SourcesShared/VortXEdgeAuth.swift.
app/Config/VortXEdge.xcconfig

# --- tooling / misc ---
.DS_Store
.playwright-mcp/
*.log

# agent / editor config
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
app/Resources/fonts/
graphify-out/

# Internal working docs (planning, handoff, audits, design/product context).
# Kept locally for our own use; never published to the repo.
/HANDOFF.md
/PRODUCT.md
/DESIGN.md
/docs/PLAN.md
/docs/FEATURE-PARITY.md
/docs/0.3.0-PRD.md
/docs/REVIEW-WORKLIST.md
/docs/PLATFORM-ACQUISITION.md
/docs/PLAYER-CONTROLS-DEBUG.md
/docs/REBASE-iOS.md
/docs/REBASE-stremio-core.md
/docs/superpowers/
app/*.entitlements

# runtime poster URLCache (PosterImageLoader diskPath)
app/vortx-images/
vortx-images/
